column5: This article is brutal! haha Obviously this guy doesn't fish... lol  1,100 Pound Fish Snagged  Here's a video...  <iframe width="560" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/tWuTjNvmK10" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>  Cheers, Ryan
Fish of a lifetime??,big big understatement. Could not imagine bringing in that fish!.
Incredible fish!!! The headline, not so much.
Funny indeed.  Another terrible headline would be :  "Huge crappie caught in bass hole"

Someone is trying very hard to prove Ryan wrong.  I give you:   "Rogue Ales brewery using man's beard yeast to make beer."   Type it in your search engine at your own peril, I did not click on the link, and will not.
